pull_request.title: Fixed variable initialization for hybrid sig
pull_request.body:
Fixed variable initialization that triggered a failure in hybrid sig on some platforms.

Also changed some var types to avoid potential overflows.

pull_request.title: Updated Picnic to v1.3.1
pull_request.body:
Integrated the latest version of the [optimized Picnic implementation (v1.3.1)](https://github.com/IAIK/Picnic/tree/v1.3.1).

The code (still) contains an optimized implementation of Keccak; I haven't yet replaced it with the internal OQS one. It would be desirable to also offer optimized versions os SHA3.
